parameters:
Would you like to view the event? Pink Color☆Sloppy Shooting
Course
\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Why are you in such a hurry?

\nc<Employee>Meary-san. About the member I sent this morning, we've
received a complaint from a client.

\nc<Senpai>Eh? But she's a veteran... Did she make some kind of
mistake? It was supposed to be an easy job, right?

\nc<Employee>Well, that's... they said they didn't like it and asked for
a change...
\bustMsgExp[2, 3]\nc<Senpai>That's why I'm asking, why? Don't make me ask over and over.
\nc<Employee>It's just that... the color wasn't very pretty...

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Color? Oh, I see. Succubi are supposed to be beautiful by
default... Are they looking for a perfect light pink or
something?
\nc<Employee>It seems so. Should we send her home for today?

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>What are you talking about? We're getting paid, so we have
to meet their requests. Jobs this easy don't come around
often.

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Among the recent newcomers... Saki is the only one
left.\bustMsgExp[2, 0]Saki, you take over.
\bustMsgExp[2, 3]\nc<Senpai>What, do you have a problem with that?
\nc<Saki>No, it's not that... I'm just wondering if I can do it...

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Don't worry. It's a complaint based on the client's
preference. The job itself is quite simple.
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>I see... So, what exactly should I do?

\nc<Senpai>If I remember correctly, it was just a simple shooting
course, right? The basic rule is no touching, but since it's
a high-priced course, just go along with it appropriately.
\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Eeeh!? Shooting, as in AV or something!?

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Idiot, it's nothing that exaggerated. It's just taking
photos with smartphones or something...
\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Leaks are strictly forbidden, so don't worry.

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>To think there are clients who would do such things even
after coming this far.

\nc<Senpai>They probably intend to use the photos as fap material or
something.

\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>Since they're the type to complain if they don't like
something, don't let your guard down. The shooting course is
quite pricey for what it is, and Saki, you're lucky this
time.

\bustMsgExp[1, 3]\nc<Saki>Indeed, if it's just no-touch photography, it seems easy
enough. I'll be going then!

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>Glad that's settled. Underestimating the opponent and
charging in with high spirits is part of Saki's charm, isn't
it.
\nc<Employee>...Well, this job really is quite simple...
\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>I haven't been with the company for that long either.

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>But even a difference of one or two months still makes you a
senpai, right?

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>No matter how much I do, the work never ends... What's that?
Work on a holiday?

\nc<Lewd Demon Employee>To survive, I just have to accept it... I'm not even
expecting any extra pay.
